  Changes from the original:
    - Ported the extension from Pi (@earendil-works/*) to Oh My Pi
      (@oh-my-pi/*), including the extension manifest, provider registration,
      message conversion, and config directory resolution.
    - Added a `provider.contextWindow` setting ("auto" | "1m" | "200k") that
      forces the Claude Code context window across every model, hiding models
      that have no runtime for the selected window.

